==Russian==

===Etymology===
From Russian [[по-]] ("a bit") + [[дно]] ("bottom") + the diminutive suffix '''-ок''', plural '''-ки'''.

===Noun===
'''подонки''' (podónki) {{m}} {{p}}

#[[dregs]] ''(also figurative)''
#[[riff-raff]]
#[[scum]]
#''(Singular)'' [[bastard]], [[scoundrel]]
# the [[déclassé]], [[corrupt]], [[criminal]] [[element]]s of [[society]].
#:*{{RUchar|подо́нки [[общество|о́бщества]]}} — ''dregs of society''

